    "en": {
      "title": "Demonstration in Colombo against President Ranil",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "People protest against President Ranil Wickremesinghe in front of Colombo Fort railway station.",
        "Protests and protests are taking place in many parts of the country to condemn the repression of the three forces on the Khalimugathidal protest site.",
        "In this case, the people who have gathered in front of the Colombo Fort railway station are protesting against the President and against the brutal repression carried out early this morning in Gallimugathidal."
      ],
